---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="API — Programmatic Access to Robertium Hypotheses"
  description="REST API for biomedical drug repurposing hypotheses. Query 90,000+ structured claims and 2,000+ cross-domain candidates programmatically."
  current="api"
  ogImage="/og/api.png"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div>
          <h1>API for drug repurposing research</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">Query our knowledge graph programmatically. Free for academic use, paid tiers for commercial applications.</p>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="mailto:daniel@robertium.com?subject=API%20access%20request" class="btn btn--primary">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
              Request access
            </a>
            <a href="#docs" class="btn btn--secondary">Read documentation &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="hero-card-label">Example request</div>
          <pre>{`curl -H 'Authorization: Bearer rk_live_xxx' \\
  https://api.robertium.com/v1/hypotheses\\
  ?drug_domain=epilepsy\\
  &outcome_domain=glioblastoma`}</pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--gray" id="docs">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V7.5L14.5 2z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg></div>
        <h2>What you can build</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pipeline">
        <div class="pipeline-card">
          <div class="pipe-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Validation pipelines</h3>
          <p>Cross-check hypotheses against your internal pipeline data. Test repurposing candidates programmatically before lab validation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pipeline-card">
          <div class="pipe-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Custom dashboards</h3>
          <p>Build internal tools that surface relevant hypotheses for your research domain. Real-time alerts on new candidates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pipeline-card">
          <div class="pipe-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="3"/><circle cx="5" cy="19" r="3"/><circle cx="19" cy="19" r="3"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="5" y2="16"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="19" y2="16"/><line x1="5" y1="19" x2="19" y2="19"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Knowledge graph integration</h3>
          <p>Merge Robertium graph with your proprietary data (DrugBank, ChEMBL, internal screens). Native graph format export.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg></div>
        <h2>Endpoints</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="api-endpoints">
        <div class="endpoint-block">
          <span class="endpoint-method">GET</span>/api/v1/hypotheses<br>
          <span class="endpoint-meta">Query params: drug, mediator, outcome, drug_domain, outcome_domain<br>Returns: paginated hypotheses with evidence chains</span>
        </div>
        <div class="endpoint-block">
          <span class="endpoint-method">GET</span>/api/v1/hypotheses/{'{id}'}<br>
          <span class="endpoint-meta">Returns: full hypothesis with all evidence PMIDs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="endpoint-block">
          <span class="endpoint-method">GET</span>/api/v1/claims<br>
          <span class="endpoint-meta">Query params: subject, predicate, object, domain<br>Returns: structured biomedical claims</span>
        </div>
        <div class="endpoint-block">
          <span class="endpoint-method">GET</span>/api/v1/entities/{'{name}'}<br>
          <span class="endpoint-meta">Returns: entity metadata, all claims involving entity, cross-domain occurrences</span>
        </div>
        <div class="endpoint-block">
          <span class="endpoint-method">GET</span>/api/v1/domains<br>
          <span class="endpoint-meta">Returns: list of available therapeutic domains with statistics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="endpoint-block">
          <span class="endpoint-method">POST</span>/api/v1/search<br>
          <span class="endpoint-meta">Body: {'{ query: "drugs targeting NLRP3 in neuroinflammation" }'}<br>Returns: semantic search across hypotheses (planned, Q3 2026)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>All endpoints return JSON. Authentication via API key. Rate limits depend on tier (see <a href="/pricing" style="color:#1e40af;">Pricing</a>). Public OpenAPI specification will be published with v1.0 launch.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--gray">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 019.9-1"/></svg></div>
        <h2>Authentication</h2>
      </div>
      <p>API authentication uses Bearer tokens. Request your API key after subscribing to Pro tier or higher. Academic users with .edu / institutional emails receive automatic Free tier access on request.</p>
      <div class="api-endpoints">
        <span class="endpoint-method">curl</span>-H 'Authorization: Bearer rk_live_xxxxx' \\<br>
        <span style="padding-left:20px;">https://api.robertium.com/v1/hypotheses?drug_domain=epilepsy</span>
      </div>
      <h3 style="font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1e40af; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; margin-top:24px;">Rate limits</h3>
      <ul class="simple-list">
        <li><strong>Free (Academic)</strong> — 1,000 requests/day, 10 requests/minute</li>
        <li><strong>Pro</strong> — 10,000 requests/day, 60 requests/minute</li>
        <li><strong>Enterprise</strong> — unlimited, dedicated infrastructure</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 18l6-6-6-6"/><path d="M8 6l-6 6 6 6"/></svg></div>
        <h2>SDK and tools</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Official client libraries planned for v1.0 launch:</p>
      <ul class="simple-list">
        <li><strong>Python SDK</strong> — <code style="font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:14px;">pip install robertium-py</code></li>
        <li><strong>R package</strong> — install from CRAN (computational biology focus)</li>
        <li><strong>Jupyter notebook examples</strong> — analysis templates for common research workflows</li>
        <li><strong>REST API</strong> — direct HTTP for any language</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Open-source under MIT license. Contributions welcome.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="container--narrow" style="padding:0;">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg></div>
          <h2>API status</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stats-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-num stat-num--small">Beta — Q3 2026</div>
          <div class="stat-label">current<br>status</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-num">5 / 6</div>
          <div class="stat-label">endpoints<br>designed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-num stat-num--small">September 2026</div>
          <div class="stat-label">estimated<br>launch</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container--narrow" style="padding:0; margin-top:24px;">
        <p>The API is in active development. Designed endpoints are above. Beta access opens to commercial customers in Q3 2026 alongside the first preprint publication.</p>
        <p>For early access, contact <a href="mailto:daniel@robertium.com" style="color:#1e40af;">daniel@robertium.com</a> with your use case. Early adopters get founder pricing locked in for life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="16 12 12 8 8 12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="8"/></svg></div>
        <h2>Get early access</h2>
      </div>
      <p>API keys are issued individually to early adopters. Tell us your use case — research domain, expected query volume, and integration plans — and we'll set up access tailored to your work.</p>
      <div class="data-cta">
        <a href="mailto:daniel@robertium.com?subject=Early%20API%20access%20request" class="btn btn--primary">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          Request early API access
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn--secondary">View pricing &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
